
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Pullback Playbook v3</title>
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f172a" />
  <style>
    :root{--bg:#0b1220;--panel:#121b2d;--panel2:#0f172a;--line:#24324a;--text:#edf2ff;--muted:#a8b3c7;--accent:#7c9cff;--good:#34d399;--warn:#fbbf24;--bad:#f87171;--chip:#1a2540}
    *{box-sizing:border-box} body{margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#0b1220,#09101d 45%,#0b1220);color:var(--text);font-family:Inter,system-ui,Arial,sans-serif}
    .wrap{max-width:1150px;margin:0 auto;padding:18px 14px 28px}.hero,.grid{display:grid;gap:14px}.hero{grid-template-columns:1.3fr .7fr}.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    .card{background:rgba(18,27,45,.95);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;padding:16px;box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.25)}
    h1,h2,h3,p{margin:0 0 10px} h1{font-size:1.7rem} h2{font-size:1.05rem} h3{font-size:.92rem;color:var(--muted)} p,label,small{color:var(--muted)}
    .row,.row3{display:grid;gap:10px}.row{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.row3{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr}
    textarea,input,select{width:100%;padding:12px 13px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:#0b1220;color:var(--text);font:inherit}
    textarea{min-height:105px;resize:vertical} button{border:0;padding:11px 14px;border-radius:12px;cursor:pointer;font:inherit;font-weight:700}
    .actions{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-top:10px}.primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c9cff,#8b5cf6);color:#fff}.secondary{background:#1b2742;color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--line)}.ghost{background:transparent;border:1px dashed var(--line);color:var(--muted)}
    .pillrow{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}.pill{background:var(--chip);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);border-radius:999px;padding:6px 10px;font-size:.84rem}
    .stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px}.stat{padding:12px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--panel2);border:1px solid var(--line)}.stat .big{font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text)}
    .result{display:grid;grid-template-columns:78px 1fr auto auto;gap:10px;align-items:center;padding:12px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;background:#0f172a}
    .ticker{font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.4px}.badge,.score{padding:6px 10px;border-radius:999px;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:800;white-space:nowrap}
    .watch{background:rgba(124,156,255,.18);color:#dfe8ff}.near{background:rgba(251,191,36,.18);color:#fde7a0}.ready{background:rgba(52,211,153,.18);color:#c8ffea}.avoid{background:rgba(248,113,113,.18);color:#ffd5d5}
    .s-low{background:rgba(248,113,113,.18);color:#ffd5d5}.s-mid{background:rgba(251,191,36,.18);color:#fde7a0}.s-hi{background:rgba(52,211,153,.18);color:#c8ffea}
    .list{display:grid;gap:10px;margin-top:10px}.checks{display:grid;gap:10px}.checkgroup{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:12px;background:#0f172a}.checkitem{display:flex;gap:9px;align-items:flex-start;padding:6px 0}
    .summary{background:#0f172a;border:1px dashed var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:12px;line-height:1.45}
    .mutebox{white-space:pre-wrap;background:#0f172a;border:1px dashed var(--line);border-radius:14px;padding:12px;color:var(--muted);font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.4}
    .tiny{font-size:.86rem;color:var(--muted)}.prog{height:10px;border-radius:999px;background:#0b1220;border:1px solid var(--line);overflow:hidden}.fill{height:100%;width:0;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#7c9cff,#34d399)}
    @media (max-width:900px){.hero,.grid,.row,.row3,.stats,.result{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>Pullback Playbook v3</h1>
      <p>Manual ticker entry, smarter setup scoring, auto-written summaries from the checklist, and trade planning built around your £4,000 account and £40 max risk.</p>
      <div class="pillrow"><span class="pill">Manual tickers</span><span class="pill">Auto status</span><span class="pill">Auto summary</span><span class="pill">Trade planner</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Trading Parameters</h2>
      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat"><div>Account</div><div class="big" id="accountStat">£4,000</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div>Max Risk</div><div class="big" id="riskStat">£40</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div>Risk %</div><div class="big" id="riskPctStat">1.0%</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid" style="margin-top:14px">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>1) Daily Ticker Input</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div><label>Account Size (£)</label><input id="accountSize" type="number" value="4000" min="1" /></div>
        <div><label>Max Risk (£)</label><input id="maxRisk" type="number" value="40" min="1" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row" style="margin-top:10px">
        <div><label>Market Status</label><select id="marketStatus"><option>S&P above 50 MA</option><option>S&P near 50 MA</option><option>S&P below 50 MA</option></select></div>
        <div><label>List Name</label><input id="listName" placeholder="Today's Scan" /></div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:10px"><label>Tickers</label><textarea id="tickerInput" placeholder="PWR&#10;LIN&#10;UNP&#10;DE&#10;HSY"></textarea></div>
      <div class="actions"><button class="primary" id="buildBtn">Build Cards</button><button class="secondary" id="saveBtn">Save List</button><button class="secondary" id="loadBtn">Load Saved</button><button class="ghost" id="clearBtn">Clear</button></div>
      <div class="tiny">Use one ticker per line or comma-separated. Best for phone workflow.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>2) Prompt Generator</h2>
      <p class="tiny">Use this to paste a clean watchlist prompt here in chat.</p>
      <div class="actions"><button class="primary" id="genWatchPromptBtn">Generate Watchlist Prompt</button><button class="secondary" id="copyWatchPromptBtn">Copy Prompt</button></div>
      <div id="watchPromptBox" class="mutebox" style="margin-top:10px">Your prompt will appear here.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid" style="margin-top:14px">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>3) Ranked Results</h2>
      <p class="tiny">Each ticker gets a status, score, and auto-written note from the checklist logic.</p>
      <div id="results" class="list"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>4) Setup Review</h2>
      <div class="row3">
        <div><label>Ticker</label><input id="selectedTicker" placeholder="PWR" /></div>
        <div><label>Status</label><input id="statusBox" readonly /></div>
        <div><label>Score</label><input id="scoreBox" readonly /></div>
      </div>

      <div class="checks" style="margin-top:12px">
        <div class="checkgroup">
          <h3>Trend</h3>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="trendStrong"> Strong uptrend</label>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="above50"> Above 50 MA</label>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="above200"> Above 200 MA</label>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="ma50gt200"> 50 MA above 200 MA</label>
        </div>
        <div class="checkgroup">
          <h3>Pullback + Confirmation</h3>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="near20"> Near 20 MA</label>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="near50"> Near 50 MA</label>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="stabilising"> Stabilising</label>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="bounce"> Bounce candle</label>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="volume"> Volume supportive</label>
        </div>
        <div class="checkgroup">
          <h3>Trade Plan</h3>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="entryDefined"> Entry defined</label>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="stopDefined"> Stop defined</label>
          <label class="checkitem"><input type="checkbox" class="logic" id="targetDefined"> Target defined</label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top:12px"><div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;margin-bottom:6px"><strong>Setup Quality</strong><span id="progressText">0 / 10</span></div><div class="prog"><div class="fill" id="progressFill"></div></div></div>
      <div style="margin-top:12px"><h3>Auto Summary</h3><div class="summary" id="summaryBox">No setup reviewed yet.</div></div>
      <div class="actions"><button class="primary" id="saveReviewBtn">Save Review to Card</button><button class="secondary" id="resetReviewBtn">Reset Review</button></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid" style="margin-top:14px">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>5) Trade Planner</h2>
      <div class="row3">
        <div><label>Entry</label><input id="entryPrice" type="number" step="0.01" /></div>
        <div><label>Stop</label><input id="stopPrice" type="number" step="0.01" /></div>
        <div><label>Target</label><input id="targetPrice" type="number" step="0.01" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="actions"><button class="primary" id="calcBtn">Calculate</button><button class="secondary" id="genChartPromptBtn">Generate Chart Prompt</button></div>
      <div class="stats" style="margin-top:10px">
        <div class="stat"><div>Risk / Share</div><div class="big" id="riskPerShare">–</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div>Position Size</div><div class="big" id="positionSize">–</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div>Reward / Risk</div><div class="big" id="rrValue">–</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="tiny" id="calcNote" style="margin-top:10px">Enter entry, stop, and target to calculate size.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>6) Chart Prompt</h2>
      <div class="actions"><button class="secondary" id="copyChartPromptBtn">Copy Chart Prompt</button></div>
      <div id="chartPromptBox" class="mutebox" style="margin-top:10px">Your chart prompt will appear here.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
const $ = id => document.getElementById(id);
const key = 'pullbackPlaybookV3';
const state = {accountSize:4000,maxRisk:40,marketStatus:'S&P above 50 MA',listName:"Today's Scan",tickers:[],cards:[]};

function saveState(){state.accountSize=Number($('accountSize').value||0);state.maxRisk=Number($('maxRisk').value||0);state.marketStatus=$('marketStatus').value;state.listName=$('listName').value||"Today's Scan";localStorage.setItem(key,JSON.stringify(state));renderStats();}
function loadState(){try{Object.assign(state,JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(key)||'{}')||{})}catch(e){} $('accountSize').value=state.accountSize;$('maxRisk').value=state.maxRisk;$('marketStatus').value=state.marketStatus||'S&P above 50 MA';$('listName').value=state.listName||"Today's Scan";$('tickerInput').value=(state.tickers||[]).join('\n');renderStats();renderCards();}
function renderStats(){const pct=state.accountSize?((state.maxRisk/state.accountSize)*100).toFixed(1):'0.0';$('accountStat').textContent=`£${state.accountSize.toLocaleString()}`;$('riskStat').textContent=`£${state.maxRisk.toLocaleString()}`;$('riskPctStat').textContent=`${pct}%`;}
function parseTickers(text){return [...new Set(text.split(/[\n, ]+/).map(x=>x.trim().toUpperCase()).filter(Boolean))]}
function baseCard(ticker){return {ticker,status:'Watch',score:0,summary:'No review saved yet.',checks:{},entry:'',stop:'',target:''}}
function buildCards(){saveState();state.tickers=parseTickers($('tickerInput').value);state.cards=state.tickers.map(t=>{const ex=(state.cards||[]).find(c=>c.ticker===t);return ex||baseCard(t)});localStorage.setItem(key,JSON.stringify(state));renderCards();generateWatchPrompt();}
function scoreAndStatusFromChecks(checks){const nearMA=!!(checks.near20||checks.near50),trendStrong=!!checks.trendStrong,above50=!!checks.above50,above200=!!checks.above200,ma50gt200=!!checks.ma50gt200,stabilising=!!checks.stabilising,bounce=!!checks.bounce,volume=!!checks.volume,tradePlan=!!(checks.entryDefined&&checks.stopDefined&&checks.targetDefined);let score=0;if(trendStrong)score+=2;if(above50)score+=1;if(above200)score+=1;if(ma50gt200)score+=1;if(nearMA)score+=2;if(stabilising)score+=1;if(bounce)score+=1;if(volume)score+=1;if(tradePlan)score+=1;let status='Watch';const hardFail=!above50||!above200||!nearMA||!trendStrong;if(hardFail)status='Avoid';else if(stabilising&&bounce&&tradePlan)status='Ready';else if(stabilising)status='Near Pullback';else status='Watch';return {score,status};}
function buildSummary(checks,status){const nearMA=checks.near20||checks.near50,stabilising=!!checks.stabilising,bounce=!!checks.bounce,trendStrong=!!checks.trendStrong,above50=!!checks.above50,above200=!!checks.above200;if(!trendStrong||!above50||!above200||!nearMA){let reason='The stock does not meet the basic quality pullback rules.';if(!trendStrong)reason+=' Trend quality is not strong enough.';else if(!nearMA)reason+=' Pullback location is not close enough to the 20 MA or 50 MA.';else reason+=' The broader trend structure is not strong enough.';return reason;} let a='Strong uptrend.';let b=checks.near20?' Pullback is near the 20 MA.':' Pullback is near the 50 MA.';let c=' There is no clear stabilisation or bounce yet.';if(stabilising&&!bounce)c=' Price is starting to stabilise, but the bounce is not confirmed yet.';if(stabilising&&bounce&&status==='Ready')c=' Price is stabilising and a bounce is forming. Setup is ready for entry review.';if(stabilising&&bounce&&status!=='Ready')c=' Price is stabilising and a bounce is forming, but the trade plan is not fully defined yet.';return a+b+c;}
function statusClass(status){if(status==='Ready')return'ready';if(status==='Near Pullback')return'near';if(status==='Avoid')return'avoid';return'watch'}
function scoreClass(score){if(score>=8)return's-hi';if(score>=5)return's-mid';return's-low'}
function renderCards(){const box=$('results');box.innerHTML='';if(!state.cards||!state.cards.length){box.innerHTML='<div class="summary">No cards yet. Add tickers and press Build Cards.</div>';return;} const ordered=[...state.cards].sort((a,b)=>b.score-a.score||a.ticker.localeCompare(b.ticker));ordered.forEach(card=>{const div=document.createElement('div');div.className='result';div.innerHTML=`<div class="ticker">${card.ticker}</div><div><div>${card.summary}</div></div><div class="score ${scoreClass(card.score)}">${card.score}/10</div><div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:flex-end"><span class="badge ${statusClass(card.status)}">${card.status}</span><button class="secondary" data-act="load">Load</button></div>`;div.querySelector('[data-act="load"]').onclick=()=>loadCard(card.ticker);box.appendChild(div);});}
function loadCard(ticker){const card=state.cards.find(c=>c.ticker===ticker);if(!card)return;$('selectedTicker').value=card.ticker;const c=card.checks||{};['trendStrong','above50','above200','ma50gt200','near20','near50','stabilising','bounce','volume','entryDefined','stopDefined','targetDefined'].forEach(id=>$(id).checked=!!c[id]);$('entryPrice').value=card.entry||'';$('stopPrice').value=card.stop||'';$('targetPrice').value=card.target||'';refreshReview();generateChartPrompt();calculate();}
function currentChecks(){const out={};['trendStrong','above50','above200','ma50gt200','near20','near50','stabilising','bounce','volume','entryDefined','stopDefined','targetDefined'].forEach(id=>out[id]=$(id).checked);return out;}
function refreshReview(){const checks=currentChecks();const r=scoreAndStatusFromChecks(checks);$('scoreBox').value=`${r.score}/10`;$('statusBox').value=r.status;$('summaryBox').textContent=buildSummary(checks,r.status);$('progressText').textContent=`${r.score} / 10`;$('progressFill').style.width=`${r.score*10}%`;}
function saveReview(){const ticker=$('selectedTicker').value.trim().toUpperCase();if(!ticker)return;const checks=currentChecks();const r=scoreAndStatusFromChecks(checks);const summary=buildSummary(checks,r.status);let card=state.cards.find(c=>c.ticker===ticker);if(!card){card=baseCard(ticker);state.cards.push(card);} card.checks=checks;card.score=r.score;card.status=r.status;card.summary=summary;card.entry=$('entryPrice').value||'';card.stop=$('stopPrice').value||'';card.target=$('targetPrice').value||'';localStorage.setItem(key,JSON.stringify(state));renderCards();}
function resetReview(){['selectedTicker','statusBox','scoreBox','entryPrice','stopPrice','targetPrice'].forEach(id=>$(id).value='');['trendStrong','above50','above200','ma50gt200','near20','near50','stabilising','bounce','volume','entryDefined','stopDefined','targetDefined'].forEach(id=>$(id).checked=false);$('summaryBox').textContent='No setup reviewed yet.';$('progressText').textContent='0 / 10';$('progressFill').style.width='0%';$('chartPromptBox').textContent='Your chart prompt will appear here.';$('calcNote').textContent='Enter entry, stop, and target to calculate size.';['riskPerShare','positionSize','rrValue'].forEach(id=>$(id).textContent='–');}
function calculate(){saveState();const entry=Number($('entryPrice').value),stop=Number($('stopPrice').value),target=Number($('targetPrice').value);if(!entry||!stop||entry<=stop){$('riskPerShare').textContent='–';$('positionSize').textContent='–';$('rrValue').textContent='–';$('calcNote').textContent='Entry must be above stop for a long setup.';return;} const r=entry-stop,shares=Math.floor(state.maxRisk/r),rr=target&&target>entry?(target-entry)/r:null;$('riskPerShare').textContent=r.toFixed(2);$('positionSize').textContent=shares>0?`${shares} shares`:'0 shares';$('rrValue').textContent=rr?`${rr.toFixed(2)}R`:'–';$('calcNote').textContent=shares<1?'This stop is too wide for your £40 max risk.':'Size is based on your £40 max risk. Check the chart before trading.';}
function generateWatchPrompt(){saveState();const watch=(state.tickers||[]).join('\n')||'(add tickers here)';const prompt=`Analyse these stocks for my Quality Pullback strategy.\n\nRules:\n- Prefer strong stocks in an uptrend\n- Pullback near 20MA or 50MA\n- Must stabilise or bounce\n- Previous swing high = first target\n\nAccount:\n£${state.accountSize} account\n£${state.maxRisk} max risk\n\nWatchlist:\n${watch}\n\nReturn:\nWatch / Near Pullback / Ready / Avoid\nwith a pullback score out of 10 and a one-line reason in plain English.`;$('watchPromptBox').textContent=prompt;return prompt;}
function generateChartPrompt(){saveState();const ticker=$('selectedTicker').value.trim().toUpperCase()||'[TICKER]';const prompt=`Analyse this uploaded chart for my Quality Pullback strategy.\n\nUse these rules:\n- Prefer strong stocks in an uptrend\n- Use the 20 MA, 50 MA, and volume if visible\n- I want a pullback near the 20 MA or 50 MA\n- Do not count it as valid unless price is stabilising or bouncing\n- Use previous swing high as the first target area\n- If the setup is unclear, tell me not to trade\n- Explain in plain English and avoid jargon\n\nMy account and risk rules:\n- Account size: £${state.accountSize}\n- Max risk per trade: £${state.maxRisk.toFixed(2)}\n\nContext:\n- Ticker: ${ticker}\n- Market status: ${state.marketStatus}\n- Chart file: A chart image is attached.\n\nPlease give me:\n1. Plain-English chart read\n2. Verdict: Watch / Near Entry / Entry / Avoid\n3. Suggested entry\n4. Suggested stop\n5. First target\n6. Position size based on my account and max risk\n7. One-sentence final verdict`;$('chartPromptBox').textContent=prompt;return prompt;}
async function copyText(text){try{await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text)}catch(e){}}
$('buildBtn').onclick=buildCards;$('saveBtn').onclick=()=>{buildCards();saveState()};$('loadBtn').onclick=loadState;$('clearBtn').onclick=()=>{$('tickerInput').value='';state.tickers=[];state.cards=[];localStorage.setItem(key,JSON.stringify(state));renderCards();};
$('genWatchPromptBtn').onclick=()=>{buildCards();copyText(generateWatchPrompt())};$('copyWatchPromptBtn').onclick=()=>copyText($('watchPromptBox').textContent);$('saveReviewBtn').onclick=saveReview;$('resetReviewBtn').onclick=resetReview;$('calcBtn').onclick=calculate;$('genChartPromptBtn').onclick=()=>{calculate();copyText(generateChartPrompt())};$('copyChartPromptBtn').onclick=()=>copyText(generateChartPrompt());
['accountSize','maxRisk','marketStatus','listName'].forEach(id=>$(id).addEventListener('change',saveState));document.querySelectorAll('.logic').forEach(el=>el.addEventListener('change',refreshReview));['entryPrice','stopPrice','targetPrice'].forEach(id=>$(id).addEventListener('input',calculate));
loadState();generateWatchPrompt();generateChartPrompt();
</script>
</body>
</html>
